<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kendall Jenner and Kylie Jenner flashed their cute smiles in a throwback photo with their grandmother shared Sunday on social media.</p>

<p>The photo showed a young Kendall, 24, and her little sister Kylie, 23, as girls with their maternal grandmother Mary Jo Shannon, 86.</p>

<p>The girls stood next to their grandmother who sat next to them at an outdoor table with a present in front of her.</p>

<p>Throwback photo: Kendall Jenner and Kylie Jenner flashed their cute smiles in a throwback photo with their grandmother shared Sunday on social media</p>

<p>Kylie shared the photo from a fan account on her Instagram Stories with no further comment.</p>

<p>Kendall in the snap wore a white top with geometric shapes and blue plaid trousers, while Kyle sported a leopard-print dress.</p>

<p>Mary Jo wore a matching orange top and sweater and accessorized with sunglasses.</p>

<p>Kendall and Kylie grew to fame on the reality show Keeping Up With The Kardashians that debuted on the E! network in October 2007.</p>

<p>Grown up: Kendall, shown in December 2018 in London, and Kylie, shown in August 2019 in Los Angeles, rose to fame on Keeping Up With The Kardashians</p>

<p>Reality stars: Kendall and Kylie are shown with mother Kris Jenner and half-sisters Kourtney, Khloe and Kim Kardashian in a 2007 promo still for their E! reality show</p>

<p>The Kardashians announced last week on Instagram that the show will come to an end in 2021 after 20 seasons.</p>

<p>The reality show spawned numerous spin-off including the short-lived Life Of Kylie that featured Kylie's former best friend Jordyn Woods, 22, for one season before its cancellation.</p>

<p>Mary Jo is the mother family matriarch Kris Jenner, 64, who had children Kourtney, Kim, Khloe and Robert with her late attorney husband Robert Kardashian who died in 2003 at age 59 of esophageal cancer.</p>

<p>It's over: The Kardashians, shown in 2016 in New York City, announced last week on Instagram that their family reality show will come to an end in 2021 after 20 seasons</p>

<p>Kris later had daughters Kendall and Kylie with Caitlyn Jenner, 70, formerly known as Bruce Jenner.</p>

<p>Mary Jo has appeared in multiple episodes of KUWTK with her daughter, grandchildren and great-grandchildren.</p>

<p>Kylie has a two-year-old daughter Stormi with rapper Travis Scott, 29.</p>

<p>Travis and Kylie were in a relationship from 2017 to 2019.</p>

<p>Family time: Travis Scott has a two-year-old daughter Stormi with ex Kylie, shown together in August 2019 in Santa Monica, California</p>
